                "elements": [
                    {
                        "type": "rich_text_section",
                        "elements": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "We need a language to talk about relationships represented in visual diagrams, eg “node a feeds into node b”. Once we have a language we can represent the same diagram as text. Any projection, zooming or modification of the diagram can also be done in the language oriented text version. So the question is: what does the visual diagram give us?\n\n(this is not a counterpoint but rather a request for further examination)"
